OL,6,FYou might already be aware of who is
OL,7,Ftipped for which Oscar, thanks to a
OL,8,Ftelling awards season so far - for
OL,9,Fexample, Cillian Murphy has picked up
OL,10,Fthe Golden Globe, , and a Screen
OL,11,FActors Guild Award for his performance
OL,12,Fas the titular role in Oppenheimer.
OL,14,FYou may also know that this year is
OL,15,Fthe first time the Oscars' new
OL,16,Fdiversity rules .
OL,18,FBut what might you not know about the
