OL,4,Cyou don't know about the Awards
OL,6,FWhy is the Oscar statuette worth $1?
OL,8,FEach of those iconic, shiny men cost
OL,9,Faround $500 to produce, made up of a
OL,10,Fmetal plated in copper, nickel,
OL,11,Fsilver, and 24-karat gold.
OL,13,FThe manufacturing process actually
OL,14,Fstarts a year in advance, to ensure
OL,15,Fany mistakes can be reversed in time
OL,16,Ffor the big night.
OL,18,FBut did you know they are priced at
OL,19,Fjust one single US dollar?
