OL,3,CA peek behind the Oscars curtain: What
OL,4,Cyou don't know about the Awards
OL,6,FThe 1938 Oscar of Hollywood icon Bette
OL,7,FDavis was sold at an auction for
OL,8,F$578,000 (#454,000) in 2001 to an
OL,9,Fanonymous bidder.
OL,11,FThat bidder was later confirmed to be
OL,12,Fcelebrated director Steven Spielberg.
OL,14,FWho are the Oscars' seat-fillers and
OL,15,Fwhat are their jobs?
OL,17,FWho's that person sat next to Martin
OL,18,FScorsese's wife? Turns out, it's a
OL,19,Fstranger.
