OL,3,CA peek behind the Oscars curtain: What
OL,4,Cyou don't know about the Awards
OL,6,FThat's right, you can apply to be an
OL,7,FAcademy Award seat-filler.
OL,9,FWhen the camera pans to the star-
OL,10,Fstudded crowd, organisers don't want
OL,11,Fany gaps or empty seats - the ceremony
OL,12,Fmust stay bustling, fun, and - above
OL,13,Fall - engaging.
OL,15,FSo when a winner runs up on stage to
OL,16,Faccept their award, a seat-filler is
OL,17,Fwaiting in the wings to take their
OL,18,Fspot.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/17
