OL,3,CA peek behind the Oscars curtain: What
OL,4,Cyou don't know about the Awards
OL,6,FThe people in charge use the advert
OL,7,Fbreaks to direct the seat-fillers to
OL,8,Fthe right chair.
OL,10,FSeat-fillers are also instructed to
OL,11,Ffill the gap even when guests leave
OL,12,Fthe room to drink, chat, or nip to the
OL,13,Floo.
OL,15,FWhen their services aren't needed,
OL,16,Fthey wait outside the Dolby Theatre,
OL,17,Fwhere the ceremony takes place.
OL,19,FAnd before you ask, nope - you don't
OL,20,Fget paid. Your payment is that free,
OL,21,Fgolden ticket to the Oscars.
