OL,3,CA peek behind the Oscars curtain: What
OL,4,Cyou don't know about the Awards
OL,6,FCan you refuse an Oscar?
OL,8,FYou can. And three people have done,
OL,9,Ffor varying reasons.
OL,11,FThe most famous example is Marlon
OL,12,FBrando, who in 1973 refused to accept
OL,13,Fthe best actor award for his role in
OL,14,FThe Godfather.
OL,16,FInstead, Brando - who was not in
OL,17,Fattendance - sent up 26-year-old
OL,18,Factivist, Sacheen Littlefeather, on
OL,19,Fstage to explain why he was declining
OL,20,Fto accept.
