OL,3,CA peek behind the Oscars curtain: What
OL,4,Cyou don't know about the Awards
OL,6,FLittlefeather spoke - while the crowd
OL,7,Fbooed - about how Brando's beliefs on
OL,8,Fthe industry's poor treatment of
OL,9,FNative Americans led him to reject the
OL,10,Fprize.
OL,12,FThe campaigner died in October 2022,
OL,13,Faged 75.
OL,15,FAlso on the list is George C. Scott,
OL,16,Fwho simply just did not think much of
OL,17,Fthe ceremony.
