OL,3,CA peek behind the Oscars curtain: What
OL,4,Cyou don't know about the Awards
OL,6,FHe won best actor for his performance
OL,7,Fin General George S. Patton in 1971,
OL,8,Fbut did not want the win, famously
OL,9,Fcalling the Oscars "a two-hour meat
OL,10,Fparade, a public display with
OL,11,Fcontrived suspense for economic
OL,12,Freasons."
OL,14,FBut the first ever person to refuse an
OL,15,FOscar was screenwriter Dudley Nichols.
OL,17,FIn 1936, he won best screenplay for
OL,18,FThe Informer, set during the Irish War
OL,19,FOf Independence, but he did not accept
OL,20,Fand cited the ongoing Hollywood
OL,21,Fwriters' strike as his reason.
