OL,6,FWhat's in the Oscars goodie bag?
OL,8,FIt's hard to imagine a goodie bag
OL,9,Fworth over $100,000 (#78,575), but
OL,10,Fthat's exactly what each guest will be
OL,11,Fgetting at the end of the night,
OL,12,Faccording to the people behind it.
OL,14,FNamed the "Everyone Wins" gift bag, LA-
OL,15,Fbased entertainment marketing company
OL,16,FDistinctive Assets has promised an
OL,17,Fabundance of "swag".
