OL,3,CA peek behind the Oscars curtain: What
OL,4,Cyou don't know about the Awards
OL,6,FIn past years, there have been some
OL,7,Fludicrous presents - in 2022, guests
OL,8,Fwere reportedly given an entire plot
OL,9,Fof land in Scotland.
OL,11,FIn 2024, Distinctive Assets have said
OL,12,Fpeople will be leaving with a range of
OL,13,Fsurprises, including a portable
OL,14,Fblender, a seven-day "holistic
OL,15,Fwellness retreat", 10,000 donated
OL,16,Fmeals in support of animal charity
OL,17,FPETA, and a private show with a
OL,18,Fmentalist.
