OL,6,FThat's not all - they'll also be
OL,7,Fgetting a three-day trip to a private
OL,8,Fvilla, an in-home clinical sleep
OL,9,Fconsultation, a luxury shoe bag, a
OL,10,Fportable infrared grill, and an all-
OL,11,Finclusive Swiss getaway.
OL,13,FA Scottish chocolate maker, Fiona
OL,14,FMcArthur, owner of Fetcha Chocolates,
OL,15,Fsaid she was "over the moon" after
OL,16,Fbeing chosen to make sweet treats for
OL,17,Fthe A-listers' goodie bags this year.
OL,19,FMs McArthur said she was contacted
OL,20,F"out of the blue" on LinkedIn.
