OL,6,FThe list, shockingly, doesn't end
OL,7,Fthere. The venue seats over 3,000
OL,8,Fpeople - you can do the math.
OL,10,FAre there certain phrases presenters
OL,11,Fhave to say?
OL,13,FThere are - up until 1989, each award
OL,14,Fwas announced pre-fixed by: "And the
OL,15,Fwinner is...".
OL,17,FBut this statement accrued complaints
OL,18,F- nominees felt that it was not fair
OL,19,Fto peg one person a "winner" and the
OL,20,Frest "losers".
