OL,3,CA peek behind the Oscars curtain: What
OL,4,Cyou don't know about the Awards
OL,6,FPerformances, soundtracks, scripts,
OL,7,Fand everything else are nuanced. It
OL,8,Fdepends on the premise of the film,
OL,9,Fthe tone, and often, the budget.
OL,11,FFrom the 61st Academy Awards onwards,
OL,12,Fevery single presenter is required to
OL,13,Finstead say the familiar line: "And
OL,14,Fthe Oscar goes to...".
