OL,3,CA peek behind the Oscars curtain: What
OL,4,Cyou don't know about the Awards
OL,6,FIt's a spot that everyone wants - and
OL,7,Fproves a lucrative deal for those in
OL,8,Fcharge. After all, an average of 18.7
OL,9,Fmillion people watched 2023's event.
OL,11,FIn 2018, the average cost for a 30-
OL,12,Fsecond commercial during the broadcast
OL,13,Fwas $1.6m each.
OL,15,FIt then raised to $1.9m in 2017 and in
OL,16,F2022, the average price of a spot
OL,17,Faired during the Academy Awards was
OL,18,F$2.2m (#1.7m).
